{"tid":1710950,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［千奇唔好］狗仔宿舍先係開花要點","createTime":"2019-11-12T09:19:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T17:53:10.000Z","uid":403,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b3023f0c30ef3b635a764a41b35a7ce99891c997","tid":1710950,"uid":403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T09:19:37.000Z","msg":"千奇唔可以打狗仔宿舍<br />\n<br />\n狗仔打我地就齊裝屠殺<br />\n我地打佢仔女老婆老豆老母 變左係我地屠佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ed53d61661bb1184a8985b12ad13b2f57404a2c","tid":1710950,"uid":48251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T09:20:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5b1a79881478f84de0cfba8938b002ab22a1f7e5","tid":1710950,"uid":330842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T09:20:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"206780d9f316987dc471d161559a28f928ad1c01","tid":1710950,"uid":76404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T09:20:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b75d6e5a72a3c230555fc8831721455e20139ef5","tid":1710950,"uid":403,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T09:22:43.000Z","msg":"另外申請左禁制令 大家唔好犯法<br />\n<br />\n律政司一方納入禁令的紀律部隊/已婚警察宿舍：<br />\n<br />\n紀律部隊宿舍：<br />\n1）豐盛街紀律部隊宿舍<br />\n2）高翔苑<br />\n3）葵馥苑<br />\n4）葵蓉苑<br />\n5）荔景紀律部隊宿舍<br />\n6）秀茂坪紀律部隊宿舍<br />\n7）上水紀律部隊宿舍<br />\n8）順利紀律部隊宿舍<br />\n9）西九龍紀律部隊宿舍<br />\n10）黃大仙紀律部隊宿舍<br />\n11）油美苑<br />\n<br />\n已婚警察宿舍：<br />\n1）青山政府宿舍<br />\n2）柴灣已婚警察宿舍<br />\n3）奥卑利街已婚警察宿舍<br />\n4）黃竹坑警察學院已婚警察宿舍<br />\n5）上水已婚警察宿舍<br />\n6）大欖水警基地幫辨宿舍<br />\n7）青衣已婚警察宿舍<br />\n8）屯門湖康警察宿舍<br />\n9）西區已婚警察宿舍<br />\n10）元朗已婚警察宿舍"},{"pid":"04c4300f718124bace54e6084d61f4f1430d6442","tid":1710950,"uid":28831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T09:23:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ef98c7cbc99ae945a1a5cbd59511f30313f2b27d","tid":1710950,"uid":201725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim